<text top="209" left="57" width="121" height="11" font="3"><b>Human Rights Council </b></text>
<text top="223" left="57" width="98" height="9" font="4"><b>Thirty-seventh session </b></text>
<text top="235" left="57" width="117" height="9" font="1">26 February–23 March 2018 </text>
<text top="247" left="57" width="66" height="9" font="1">Agenda item 10 </text>
